('deal-010','Kassenzone','Felix Weber','https://linkedin.com/in/felix-weber-kassenzone','series-a','€12M',12000000,'Germany','passed','Round too large for our fund size. We cannot lead at €12M and they want a lead. Introduced to Headline and HV Capital.','Francesco','referral','2026-01-20','Checkout infrastructure for German e-commerce. Great metrics (€2M ARR, 4x growth) but round size exceeds our check capacity.','["ecommerce","infrastructure","germany","too-large"]'),
