('deal-015','FleetPulse','Thomas Braun','https://linkedin.com/in/thomas-braun-fleetpulse','series-a','€10M',10000000,'Germany','passed','Valuation too high. Asking €50M pre-money on €1.5M ARR is too aggressive for a fleet management tool. Metrics do not justify the ask.','Francesco','email','2026-02-01','Fleet management + predictive maintenance for logistics companies. Good product, but valuation expectations misaligned with traction.','["logistics","fleet","iot","overpriced"]'),
