('deal-017','Nexora Robotics','Prof. Martin Keller','https://linkedin.com/in/martin-keller-nexora','seed','€5M',5000000,'Germany','rejected','Hardware-heavy business model. We focus on software/SaaS. Capital intensity of robotics manufacturing does not fit our fund strategy.','Francesco','event','2026-01-15','Warehouse robotics for last-mile fulfillment. TU Munich spinoff. Impressive tech but requires €50M+ to scale manufacturing.','["robotics","logistics","hardware","deeptech"]'),
('deal-018','StudyBuddy','Amelie Wagner','https://linkedin.com/in/amelie-wagner-studybuddy','pre-seed','€300K',300000,'Germany','rejected','EdTech B2C is extremely hard to monetize. No clear path to €1M ARR. Founder passionate but business model unproven. Advised to consider B2B pivot.','Matilda','website','2026-03-10','AI study companion for university students. Nice UX, 8k student users, but zero revenue and unclear monetization.','["edtech","b2c","students","ai"]'),
